e>` \n- 或者使用 `@ObservedObject` 的擦除包装\n\n最简单的方案是让 `ContentView` 仍然用 `AppState` 具体类型，但通过初始化注入。`PreviewWindowController` 持有协议类型。\n\n## 文件位置\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppState.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppWindowManager.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppDelegate.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/ContentView.swift`\n\n## 验证\n完成修改后运行：\n```bash\ncd /Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare && swift build\nswift test\n```\n\n确保编译通过，测试通过。","uuid":"6556e3fb-da7a-41e0-bb63-3fd9da5227d8","session_id":"41c019a8-071d-4d72-b209-d88f767a956d"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你是 Swift 重构专家。请执行 AppState 协议注入重构。\n\n## 任务\n重构 `AppState` 和相关类型，使用协议注入替代直接依赖，消除耦合。\n\n## 当前架构问题\n1. `AppWindowManager.openWindow()` 直接创建 `AppState()` - 紧耦合\n2. `PreviewWindowController` 直接持有 `AppState` 类型\n3. `ContentView` 直接使用 `@ObservedObject var appState: AppState` - 无法测试\n\n## 目标架构\n1. 定义 `AppStateProtocol` 协议\n2. `AppState` 遵循该协议\n3. `PreviewWindowController` 和 `ContentView` 使用 `any AppStateProtocol`\n4. `AppWindowManager` 通过工厂创建\n\n## 具体修改\n\n### 1. AppState.swift - 添加协议\n```swift\nprotocol AppStateProtocol: ObservableObject {\n    associatedtype Document: Identifiable\n    var id: UUID { get }\n    var document: Document? { get }\n    var errorMessage: String? { get set }\n    var windowTitle: String { get }\n    var renderMode: MarkdownRenderMode { get set }\n    func reload()\n    func open(url: URL)\n    func save(text: String)\n}\n\nextension AppState {\n    struct Document: Identifiable {\n        let id = UUID()\n        let url: URL\n        var rawText: String\n    }\n}\n```\n\n注意：`AppState.Document` 需要暴露给协议使用。\n\n### 2. AppWindowManager.swift\n- 添加 `AppStateFactory` 协议\n- 默认实现使用 `DefaultAppStateFactory` 创建 `AppState`\n- `shared` 持有工厂实例\n- `openWindow` 使用工厂创建\n\n### 3. PreviewWindowController.swift\n- 改为 `let appState: any AppStateProtocol`\n- 初始化签名改为接收 `any AppStateProtocol`\n\n### 4. ContentView.swift\n- `@ObservedObject var appState: AppState` 无法直接改为协议\n- 方案：保持 `@ObservedObject` 但在视图层使用类型擦除\n- 或者：使用泛型 `some AppStateProtocol` \n- 实际方案：保持 `ContentView` 使用具体 `AppState`，通过 `PreviewWindowController` 注入时使用协议\n\n关键点：`ContentView` 需要 `@ObservedObject` 来响应状态变化，所以它必须使用具体类型。但 `PreviewWindowController` 可以持有协议类型并传递给 `ContentView` 时进行类型标注。\n\n实际上更好的方案：\n- `PreviewWindowController` 持有 `any AppStateProtocol`\n- `ContentView` 使用泛型 `ContentView<AppState>` \n- 或者使用 `@ObservedObject` 的擦除包装\n\n最简单的方案是让 `ContentView` 仍然用 `AppState` 具体类型，但通过初始化注入。`PreviewWindowController` 持有协议类型。\n\n## 文件位置\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppState.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppWindowManager.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/AppDelegate.swift`\n- `/Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare/Sources/MarkdownPreview/ContentView.swift`\n\n## 验证\n完成修改后运行：\n```bash\ncd /Users/josh_folder/harness-simple/creator-test/markdown-tool-bare && swift build\nswift test\n```\n\n确保编译通过，测试通过。"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_function_goocvjbg6frx_1","session_id":"41c019a8-071d-4d72-b209-d88f767a956d","uuid":"9168caa9-5d5a-44d2-85d3-d08e2416c35e","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:07:30.933Z"}
